Statewave benchmark fork
========================

This project is a fork of mem0's memory-benchmark suite:
    https://github.com/mem0ai/memory-benchmarks
Original work Copyright (c) mem0ai, licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0 (see the LICENSE file).

Modifications by the Statewave team (2026), per Apache 2.0 section 4(b):
  - Added a Statewave retrieval adapter (benchmarks/common/statewave_client.py)
    and a `--backend statewave` dispatch across the benchmark runners.
  - Harness fixes to the mem0 cloud/OSS clients: cloud v3 add URL, OSS v2
    search-filter semantics, OSS message-content date grounding, and
    concurrency in the BEAM ingestion loop.
  - statewave_results/: a head-to-head comparison of Statewave, mem0 cloud,
    and mem0 OSS, plus the writeup and charts.

